00:19:59.180 --> 00:20:03.070
So we can rewrite this
just by doing some algebra

00:20:03.070 --> 00:20:05.210
on the denominator, which
is called completing

00:20:05.210 --> 00:20:06.820
the square for
reasons that you'll

00:20:06.820 --> 00:20:09.270
see when I write
