00:21:57.806 --> 00:21:59.180
The next step
which is important,

00:21:59.180 --> 00:22:01.200
is to get the limits
of integration right,

00:22:01.200 --> 00:22:03.040
because with this
definite integral method

00:22:03.040 --> 00:22:05.456
