00:22:16.130 --> 00:22:18.560
x is equal to minus alpha.

00:22:18.560 --> 00:22:20.180
So the lower limit
of integration

00:22:20.180 --> 00:22:22.770
expressed as a value
of x is minus alpha.

00:22:25.600 --> 00:22:28.770
And the upper limit
expressed as x

00:22:28.770 --> 00:22:31.890
was a tilde f, and
